A '''Moonshee''' is an [[India]]n teacher of [[languages]], especially [[Hindustani]] and [[Persian language|Persian]].

[[R. K. Kochhar]] notes that ''"the term moonshee was used by the British for [[Muslim]] [[harkaras]]"''<sup>[2]</sup>.

